Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be3\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\pos(680,200)\fn@汉仪玄宋 55S\frz270\fad(600,600)}夜阑一片白
